      <title>阿克萨姆伍德称，特斯拉股价将因自动驾驶出租车而飙升 10 倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/tesla-stock-will-surge-10-fold-on-robotaxi-ark-s-wood-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ark Investment Management LLC 的 Cathie Wood 表示，特斯拉公司组建自动驾驶出租车平台将推动其股价上涨约 10 倍，这与多年来对该汽车制造商尚未实现的业务的乐观预测相呼应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/tesla-stock-will-surge-10-fold-on-robotaxi-ark-s-wood-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 00:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
